                <summary>Mrs. Elizabeth S. Johnson, wife of Robert Johnson, died in Staunton on
                    December 22nd. She was 62 years old. She was a long-time member of the Episcopal
                    Church. "In all the relations of life, she well sustained the character of a
                    modest woman, affectionate daughter, devoted wife and fond mother, and set an
                    example worth of emulation. The distressed husband and family should look upon
                    their great loss, as her infinite gain."</summary>
